{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#E3000F; outline: 2px solid;'> </div> !} **CCF:** {!</td><td>!} [+ ccf_r_disp +] seats {!</td><td>!} [+ str_change_ccf_r +] {!</td></tr>!}

{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#0015BC'> </div> !} LPC: {!</td><td>!} [+ lpc_r_disp +] seats {!</td><td>!} [+ str_change_lpc_r +] {!</td></tr>!}

{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#0015BC'> </div> !} RPC: {!</td><td>!} [+ rpc_r_disp +] seats {!</td><td>!} [+ str_change_rpc_r +] {!</td></tr>!}

{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#0015BC'> </div> !} CPC: {!</td><td>!} [+ cpc_r_disp +] seats {!</td><td>!} [+ str_change_cpc_r +] {!</td></tr>!}

{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#0015BC'> </div> !} SCP: {!</td><td>!} [+ scp_r_disp +] seats {!</td><td>!} [+ str_change_scp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}

{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#0015BC'> </div> !} NSDAP: {!</td><td>!} [+ nsdap_r_disp +] seats {!</td><td>!} [+ str_change_nsdap_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
 
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#a0a0a0'> </div> !} Others: {!</td><td>!} [+ other_r_disp +] seats {!</td><td>!} [+ str_change_other_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}

@house_menu

- @house_simple_majority
- @house_super_majority
- @house_defeat
- @house_tie

@house_simple_majority
title: CCF gain a majority in the House
subtitle: CCF: [+ ccf_r +] seats
view-if: house_majority = 2

The CCF have secured a majority in the House of Commons.

@house_super_majority
title: CCF secure a supermajority
subtitle: CCF: [+ ccf_r +] seats
view-if: house_majority = 3

With two-thirds of the House, CCF now wield veto-proof power

@house_defeat
title: CCF lose the House
subtitle: CCF: [+ ccf_r +] seats
view-if: lpc_r > ccf_r

The LPC have taken control of the House of Commons.

@house_tie
title: The House is tied!
subtitle: Both parties are neck and neck
view-if: ccf_r = lpc_r

A tied House will cause major legislative deadloc